  <div class="accordion-section-header">
    <h2 class="accordion-title">Need Help? We've Got You Covered</h2>
    <p class="accordion-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about shipping, payments, and returns below.</p>
  </div>

  <details class="accordion-item">
    <summary>
      <span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path fill="currentColor" d="M5.5 14a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.45 2H15V6H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8h1.05a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.45-2m0 5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.45-2H1V8a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h11a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2h3l3 4v5h-2.05a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-4.9 0h-7.1a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.45 2m0-4A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 4 16.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 5.5 18A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 7 16.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 5.5 15m12-1a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.45 2H21v-3.68l-.24-.32H16v2.5c.42-.31.94-.5 1.5-.5m0 1a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5M16 9v2h4l-1.5-2z"/>
        </svg>
        Shipping Information</span
      >
      <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="accordion-content">
      <p>We offer free shipping on all orders over ₹2,00,000. Estimated delivery: 3–5 business days.</p>
      <p>
        Standard delivery takes 3–7 business days depending on your location. Express delivery options may be available
        at checkout.
      </p>
      <p>Once your order is shipped, you’ll receive a tracking number via email or SMS.</p>
      <p>Shipping is free on orders over ₹2,000. Smaller orders will include a nominal fee at checkout.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="accordion-item">
    <summary>
      <span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path fill="currentColor" d="M3.5 3A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1 5.5V6h14v-.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 12.5 3zM15 7H1v3.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 3.5 13h9a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5-2.5zm-4.5 3h2a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-2a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1"/>
        </svg>
        Payment Methods</span
      >
      <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="accordion-content">
      <p>We accept major credit cards, UPI, Paytm, Net Banking, and Cash on Delivery (COD).</p>
      <p>Net Banking is available across all leading Indian banks.</p>
      <p>COD may include a nominal handling fee.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="accordion-item">
    <summary>
      <span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20.198 3.002H3.802c-.75 0-1.126 0-1.386.177a1 1 0 0 0-.31.338c-.153.273-.116.64-.041 1.376c.125 1.228.187 1.842.513 2.28c.163.22.369.403.606.54c.476.277 1.102.277 2.355.277h12.922c1.253 0 1.879 0 2.355-.277c.237-.137.443-.32.606-.54c.326-.438.388-1.052.513-2.28c.075-.736.112-1.103-.04-1.376a1 1 0 0 0-.311-.338c-.26-.177-.636-.177-1.386-.177m-10.198 8h4m.539 4.976l2.727-.053c1.086-.02 3.237.247 3.237 2.503c0 2.34-2.249 2.57-3.262 2.57H8.05c-2.128 0-5.048-.472-5.048-4.488V7.997m11.536 7.981a.77.77 0 0 1 .232-.538l1.714-1.454m-1.946 1.992a.77.77 0 0 0 .234.579l1.712 1.414m4.495-9.974v5.028"/>
        </svg>
        Return & Refund Policy</span
      >
      <svg class="accordion-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="accordion-content">
      <p>Returns accepted within 7 days of delivery. Refunds processed in 5–7 business days.</p>
      <p>Products must be unused, with original packaging and tags intact.</p>
      <p>Exchanges can be processed if preferred over refunds.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{% style %}
  .custom-accordion-wrapper {
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
    font-family: inherit;
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-bottom : 5rem;
  }

  .accordion-section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .accordion-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .accordion-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .accordion-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-item span {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 5px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .accordion-item span svg {
   color: #721c37;
    
  }

  .accordion-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .accordion-item summary {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    list-style: none;
    background: #fff;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-item[open] summary {
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }

  .accordion-item summary:hover {
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .accordion-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-item[open] .accordion-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .accordion-content {
    padding: 0 2.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  /* Responsive Styles */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .custom-accordion-wrapper {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .accordion-title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .custom-accordion-wrapper {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }
    .accordion-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    .accordion-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .accordion-content {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .accordion-item summary {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .accordion-icon {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}
